{"tid":2389230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇英國手足做緊NHS Volunteer Responder？","createTime":"2021-01-31T17:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T10:58:21.000Z","uid":127052,"like":136,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"12401cb26f551192ccc5f5788943d0b699a9460d","tid":2389230,"uid":127052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:34:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nhsvolunteerresponders.org.uk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnhsvolunteerresponders.org.uk%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=da2c6348\" target=\"_blank\">https://nhsvolunteerresponders.org.uk/</a><br />\n<br />\n做咗幾個月 <br />\n其實都幾輕鬆<br />\n我個Role係幫人去買餸 <br />\n去藥方拎藥 幫醫院送吓物資<br />\n通常你收到Order 可以揀做唔做<br />\n做就打個電話過去 問佢要乜<br />\n真係花30分鐘左右 就做完一個Task<br />\n<br />\n最近有時間 專登做多幾單<br />\n喺Volunteer個Profile提吓自己係香港人<br />\n我諗英國人知道 我哋唔係嚟拎褔利 <br />\n我哋都想融入社會 作出貢獻<br />\n<br />\n未Sign Up嘅手足可以Sign Up<br />\n程序好簡單<br />\n同埋 基本上有車 就做到佢大部份嘅Role<br />\n通常都係 10 Miles 以內 <br />\n有時幾日先一個Call 因為都唔少Volunteer<br />\n同埋有啲Expenses可以Claim返 <br />\n<br />\n有興趣知嘅 留個言<br />\n可以答吓問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b1eab9b70ad10496275cca61a1d4906faa3fde","tid":2389230,"uid":73567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12401cb26f551192ccc5f5788943d0b699a9460d","tid":2389230,"uid":127052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:34:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nhsvolunteerresponders.org.uk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnhsvolunteerresponders.org.uk%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GwQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=da2c6348\" target=\"_blank\">https://nhsvolunteerresponders.org.uk/</a><br />\n<br />\n做咗幾個月 <br />\n其實都幾輕鬆<br />\n我個Role係幫人去買餸 <br />\n去藥方拎藥 幫醫院送吓物資<br />\n通常你收到Order 可以揀做唔做<br />\n做就打個電話過去 問佢要乜<br />\n真係花30分鐘左右 就做完一個Task<br />\n<br />\n最近有時間 專登做多幾單<br />\n喺Volunteer個Profile提吓自己係香港人<br />\n我諗英國人知道 我哋唔係嚟拎褔利 <br />\n我哋都想融入社會 作出貢獻<br />\n<b